<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Master Model Release – <%= ((user && user.username) ? user.username : ((modelUser && modelUser.username) ? modelUser.username : 'Model')) %></title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; margin: 20px; line-height: 1.4; }
    h1, h2 { margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.4rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1.2rem; }
    .meta { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    ul { margin-top: 0.4rem; }
    li { margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .note { margin-top: 1.2rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #555; }
    @media print { button { display: none; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%
    const u = (user || modelUser || {});
    const mr = (masterRelease || release || null);
  %>

  <button onclick="window.print()">Print</button>

  <h1>LumenNyx Studios – Master Model Release Record</h1>
  <div class="meta">
    Username: <strong><%= u.username || '—' %></strong><br>
    Generated: <%= new Date().toLocaleString() %>
  </div>

  <% if (!mr) { %>
    <p>No master release is on file for this model.</p>
  <% } else { %>
    <h2>Signature Record</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Signed name (digital):</strong> <%= mr.signed_name %></li>
      <li><strong>Signed at (UTC):</strong> <%= mr.signed_at %></li>
      <li><strong>IP Address:</strong> <%= mr.ip_address || '—' %></li>
      <li><strong>User-Agent:</strong> <%= mr.user_agent || '—' %></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Release Summary (Plain Language)</h2>
    <p>This model has agreed to the LumenNyx Studios master release, which includes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Certification of being at least 18 years old with valid ID.</li>
      <li>Voluntary participation with the right to stop at any time.</li>
      <li>No hidden cameras; all recording is announced or visible.</li>
      <li>Grant of rights to record, edit, distribute, and monetize performances.</li>
      <li>Understanding that full removal of content from the internet cannot be guaranteed.</li>
      <li>Independent contractor status and responsibility for personal taxes.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="note">
      This page records the electronic signature and timestamp for the master release.
      A printout may be signed physically if desired for redundancy, but the digital record remains the primary log.
    </p>
  <% } %>
</body>
</html>
